# Important Conditions

* Credit limit is determined individually based on farming operations.
* Annual review is mandatory for continuation and enhancement.
* Prompt repayment is required to receive the additional interest incentive.
* Credit can be used only for approved agricultural and allied purposes.
* RuPay Kisan Card is issued by participating banks.
* Applications can be submitted digitally through JanSamarth. ([SBI Bank][4])

